data.description: This stunning property built in 1940 has curb appeal and character like no other. It offers over 3400 sqft of prestigious features and more. The kitchen has been fully updated with a chef style appliances such as a 6-burner range, professional series refrigerator, ice maker, and dishwasher. Kitchen counter tops are soapstone including a massive island that seat up to four comfortably, that opens to the dining area. The basement is a fully finished living space with 2 bedrooms, bathroom, bar area, and laundry room. The primary suit offers a full walk-in closet with a primary balcony. The bathroom has been updated with a walk-in shower, a soaker tub with elegant light fixtures. This home also offers a 700 sqft in lawsuit on the back side of the property that was in process of being updated. It can be used for as alternate income as well or extended guest. Also located in the back yard is a pavilion, indoor heated pool with a sauna and plenty of space for kids, pets and entertaining events. This HOME IS JUST GORGEOUS!
